---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="site-footer glass">
  <div class="container footer-content">
    <div class="footer-meta">
      <div class="footer-logo">
        <span class="f-logo-icon">🇪🇺</span>
        <span class="f-logo-text">PhD<span class="highlight">Europe</span></span>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-desc">An interactive, serverless decision platform mapping PhD funding models, employment benefits, and living cost sustainabilities for early-stage researchers in Europe.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-sources">
      <h4 class="sources-title">Data Sources & Citations</h4>
      <ul class="sources-list">
        <li>Academic salaries correspond to national collective agreements (e.g., German TV-L E13, Dutch VSNU, Swedish Doktorandtrappa, UKRI minimum stipends).</li>
        <li>Tuition fee assessments reflect general state university guidelines for doctoral registrations as of 2025/2026.</li>
        <li>Cost of living estimates compile rent, food, transport, and mandatory insurance data from Numbeo, national student unions, and university advice portals.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <div class="container bottom-container">
      <span class="copyright">© 2026 PhD Europe Match Platform. No rights reserved (Public Domain).</span>
      <span class="credit">Built entirely client-side with Astro & Vanilla JS.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    margin: 40px 24px 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 40px 0 0;
    margin-top: auto; /* Push to bottom */
  }
  
  .footer-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .footer-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1.8fr;
      gap: 60px;
    }
  }
  
  .footer-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  
  .footer-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .f-logo-icon {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  
  .footer-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .footer-sources {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  
  .sources-title {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  .sources-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  
  .sources-list li {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  
  .sources-list li::before {
    content: "▪";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-hover);
  }
  
  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 20px 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .bottom-container {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .copyright {
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .credit {
    font-weight: 400;
  }
</style>
